title: Lucky Bastards S01E01 Crushing It WS DSR x264-[NY2] mp4
description:
Living in New York, you've got to have a great group of guy friends. Esquire Network introduces viewers to six men who, after decades of friendship, are right where they started: hanging out together and taking advantage of every opportunity New York City has to offer. LUCKY BASTARDS, a new 10-part original series from Esquire Network, premieres Wednesdays at 10P E/P, beginning April 16. (Source: Esquire Network)

Episode 1
 Adam moves from LA to New York were he is welcomed with a party. Rocco's father has to deal out a dose of tough love.
